        <h3>Accessibility from the outset</h3>
        <p>I'm a big advocate for accessibility and it's been considered from the start of the design and build. Due to VPN issues, our assistive tech users can't access our development environment, but I conducted an interview with an expert screen reader user and got them to demo examples of some calculator functionality similar to what we were designing and get their expertise on how best to build it and read out values. I also built a desktop prototype we tested with a screen magnification user and voice activated tech user.</p>
